      "rationale": "ANSYS Mechanical 2024R1 used as the FE solver. Vendor-supplied V&V documentation (ANSYS QA suite, ISO 9001:2015 certification) reviewed and confirmed compliant. Internal configuration management log tracks solver version, patch history, and run-environment checksums. All simulation scripts version-controlled in Git with tagged releases. Exceeds MRL 3 requirement; Gradation 3 achieved through documented SQA plan with traceability to solver release notes."
