      "rationale": "Numerical code verification performed using three benchmark problems from NAFEMS LE1, LE10, and T3 test suites. Cantilever beam bending, thick-walled cylinder under pressure, and thermal stress benchmark all reproduced to within 0.5% of analytic solutions. Patch test passed for all element types employed (C3D10 quadratic tetrahedral). Results documented in verification report NCV-2025-001."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
