      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/nagaraja-ortho-ac-eip",
      "rationale": "Equivalency between validation test conditions and COU conditions formally assessed via parameter mapping table. Loading magnitude and direction: ISO 7206-4 protocol covers 98% of the clinical loading envelope per published gait data. Geometry: validation specimens are production-representative implants (same lot, same surface treatment). Material: coupon specimens from same material batch as validation implants. Identified gaps (in vivo muscle force co-contraction not replicated in bench test) bounded by sensitivity analysis showing < 5% effect on peak stem stress. Equivalency assessment documented in report EIP-2025-001."
    }
